text: The High End of Low is the seventh studio album by American rock band, Marilyn Manson. It was released on May 20, 2009. The producers of the album were Sean Beavan, Marilyn Manson, Chris Vrenna and Jeordie White. Some critics said that they praised the album for showing a more human Manson after following his divorce, and is a return to the sound of the well-received Mechanical Animals. ==Songs== ==References== Category:2009 albums Category:Marilyn Manson albums Category:Glam rock albums Category:Heavy metal albums
